<h2>Policies</h2>
<p>Policies are {{ world.policyDuration }}-tick enhancements to your kingdom.  Policies allow you to focus on specific aspects to growing your kingdom, be it economy, defense, or war.</p>

<table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
{% for policy in world.kingdomPolicies %}
    <tr>
        <td>{{ policy.name }}</td>
        <td>{{ policy.description }}</td>
    </tr>
{% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>